<div
    id="productModal"
    class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center bg-slate-950/50 p-4"
>
    <div
        class="max-h-[92vh] w-full max-w-5xl overflow-y-auto rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl"
    >
        <div
            class="sticky top-0 z-10 flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-100 bg-white px-6 py-4"
        >
            <div>
                <h2
                    id="productModalTitle"
                    class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950"
                >
                    Thêm sản phẩm
                </h2>

                <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
                    Slug sẽ được hệ thống tự tạo từ tên sản phẩm. Ảnh đại diện dùng upload file.
                </p>
            </div>

            <button
                type="button"
                class="close-product-modal grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200"
            >
                <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
            </button>
        </div>

        <form
            id="productForm"
            class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 p-6 lg:grid-cols-3"
        >
            <input type="hidden" id="productId" />

            <div class="space-y-5 lg:col-span-2">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
                    <label class="block">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            Tên sản phẩm
                        </span>

                        <input
                            id="nameInput"
                            type="text"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                            placeholder="Nhập tên sản phẩm"
                        />

                        <small
                            data-error="nameInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>

                    <label class="block">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            SKU
                        </span>

                        <input
                            id="skuInput"
                            type="text"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                            placeholder="VD: IP16PM-256"
                        />

                        <small
                            data-error="skuInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>

                    <label class="block">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            Danh mục
                        </span>

                        <select
                            id="categoryInput"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                        >
                            <option value="">Chọn danh mục</option>
                        </select>

                        <small
                            data-error="categoryInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>

                    <label class="block">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            Trạng thái
                        </span>

                        <select
                            id="statusInput"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-white px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                        >
                            <option value="active">Đang bán</option>
                            <option value="inactive">Đang ẩn</option>
                            <option value="out_of_stock">Hết hàng</option>
                        </select>

                        <small
                            data-error="statusInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>

                    <label class="block">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            Giá bán
                        </span>

                        <input
                            id="priceInput"
                            type="number"
                            min="0"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                            placeholder="0"
                        />

                        <small
                            data-error="priceInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>

                    <label class="block">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            Giá khuyến mãi
                        </span>

                        <input
                            id="salePriceInput"
                            type="number"
                            min="0"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                            placeholder="Bỏ trống nếu không giảm giá"
                        />

                        <small
                            data-error="salePriceInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>

                    <label class="block md:col-span-2">
                        <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                            Số lượng tồn kho
                        </span>

                        <input
                            id="quantityInput"
                            type="number"
                            min="0"
                            class="mt-2 h-11 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                            placeholder="0"
                        />

                        <small
                            data-error="quantityInput"
                            class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                        ></small>
                    </label>
                </div>

                <label class="block">
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                        Mô tả ngắn
                    </span>

                    <textarea
                        id="shortDescriptionInput"
                        rows="3"
                        class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                        placeholder="Nhập mô tả ngắn của sản phẩm"
                    ></textarea>

                    <small
                        data-error="shortDescriptionInput"
                        class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                    ></small>
                </label>

                <label class="block">
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                        Mô tả chi tiết
                    </span>

                    <textarea
                        id="descriptionInput"
                        rows="5"
                        class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 px-3 py-2 text-sm outline-none focus:border-kigen-500"
                        placeholder="Nhập mô tả chi tiết"
                    ></textarea>

                    <small
                        data-error="descriptionInput"
                        class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                    ></small>
                </label>
            </div>

            <div class="space-y-4">
                <label class="block">
                    <span class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
                        Ảnh đại diện
                    </span>

                    <input
                        id="thumbnailFile"
                        type="file"
                        accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp"
                        class="mt-2 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-200 p-2 text-sm"
                    />

                    <small
                        data-error="thumbnailFile"
                        class="mt-1 block text-xs font-semibold text-rose-600"
                    ></small>
                </label>

                <img
                    id="thumbnailPreview"
                    src="https://placehold.co/600x600/f0fdfa/0f766e?text=Product"
                    alt="Product thumbnail preview"
                    class="aspect-square w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 object-cover"
                />

                <div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
                    <p class="font-bold text-slate-800">
                        Lưu ý ảnh
                    </p>

                    <p class="mt-1 leading-6">
                        Chỉ hỗ trợ JPG, PNG, WEBP. Dung lượng tối đa 2MB.
                        Nếu sửa sản phẩm mà không chọn ảnh mới, hệ thống giữ ảnh cũ.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div
                class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-3 border-t border-slate-100 pt-5 sm:flex-row sm:justify-end lg:col-span-3"
            >
                <button
                    type="button"
                    class="close-product-modal rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-100"
                >
                    Hủy
                </button>

                <button
                    id="saveProductBtn"
                    type="submit"
                    class="rounded-2xl bg-kigen-600 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-kigen-700 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-60"
                >
                    Lưu sản phẩm
                </button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>
</div>

<div
    id="detailModal"
    class="fixed inset-0 z-50 hidden items-center justify-center bg-slate-950/50 p-4"
>
    <div class="w-full max-w-4xl rounded-3xl bg-white shadow-2xl">
        <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between border-b border-slate-100 px-6 py-4"
        >
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-950">
                Chi tiết sản phẩm
            </h2>

            <button
                id="closeDetailModal"
                type="button"
                class="grid h-10 w-10 place-items-center rounded-xl bg-slate-100 text-slate-600 hover:bg-slate-200"
            >
                <i class="fa-solid fa-xmark"></i>
            </button>
        </div>

        <div
            id="detailBody"
            class="max-h-[76vh] overflow-y-auto p-6"
        ></div>
    </div>
</div>